summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 6259 for the improvement of the alley in Block 9, Plat of Aero Heights No. 2, being the alley between 38th Ave. Southwest and 39th Ave. Southwest from Southwest Graham Street to Southwest Raymond Street; and certain other alleys; by paving and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 90785 as amended by Ordinance No. 90965, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
